Making a new Angle

SextonData$AngleSq<-SextonData$Angle*SextonData$Angle

SextonAngleSq = glm(Conversion ~ Distance+AngleSq,  data = SextonData,family=binomial("logit")) 
summary(SextonAngleSq)
